The performance R package provides a unified interface to assess model fit and quality for many different statistical models. 
It is part of the growing set of tools under the easystats umbrella - a suite of R packages designed to make the use of advanced statistical techniques easy.

There are functions to report many different flavors of R-squared, Intraclass Correlation Coefficients (ICC) and checks for violations of assumptions such as overdispersion, zero-inflation or singular model fits. 

